Make a list of all the things you are grateful for.
Go for a walk or run outside.
Read a book or listen to a podcast.
Spend time with loved ones.
Do something creative, like painting, drawing, or writing.
Learn a new skill, like cooking, coding, or playing an instrument.
Volunteer your time to a cause you care about.
Clean and organize your home or workspace.
Get rid of things you don't need or use anymore.
Plan a trip or vacation.
Set some goals for yourself and make a plan to achieve them.
Take some time for yourself to relax and de-stress.
Do something that makes you happy!